		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As far as I can tell, nobody knows any of the differences.  There is only a mention of DMA and HDMA colliding on some versions of some chips.  However I have HDMA off and there is still something weird happening.
<br />
<br />There are also no case markings to tell which chips are inside.  A lower serial number (8 numbers instead of 9) may be a way to tell if it is early revs, but still not exactly which ones.  Either need to open it up, or have a game that reports the versions.

		

